style.
    .beijing {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        z-index: -1;
    }

    .rowall {
        font-family: "华文琥珀";
        width: 760px;
        height: 412px;
        position: fixed;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        margin-top: -206px;
        margin-left: -380px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .all {
        background: white;
        opacity: 0.9;
        -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 10px 15px white;
        -moz-box-shadow: 0 0 10px 15px white;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px 15px white;
        border-radius: 5px;
        display: inline-block;
        height: 412px;
        width: 380px;
        border: 1px dashed black;
        padding: 0 5px;
    }

    .wenzi {
        font-size: 40px;
        color: black;
        /*text-shadow: 0px 0px 10px red, 0px 0px 20px #FFFF00, 0px 0px 40px blue;*/
        text-shadow: 1px 1px 0 #CCC, 2px 2px 0 #CCC, 3px 3px 0 #444, 4px 4px 0 #444, 5px 5px 0 #444, 6px 6px 0 #f0f0f0;
    }

    .shenfen {
        width: 149px;
        height: 149px;
    }

    .gundong {
        position: fixed;
        bottom: 0px;
        width: 100%;
        font-size: 27px;
        font-family: "黑体";
        font-weight: bold;
        color: yellow;
    }
body
    .gundong
        marquee(direction='left', behavior='scroll', onmouseover='this.stop()', onmouseout='this.start()')
            | 游戏中请将手机静音，不要随意出入，在局玩家不得离开房间，尊重玩家发言，不要有任何场外行为，良好的游戏环境需要靠大家一起来维护。
    img.beijing(src='/pictures/baitian.png')
    .rowall
        each user,index in userList
            .all
                p.wenzi
                    span #{user.zuoWei}号玩家
                    span #{user.siyin}，身份为
                    span #{user.huiYuan}。
                img.shenfen(src="#{user.shenfen}")
